'''Alex''' is a gang member who brought his girlfriend to [[Dr. Gibson]] after she was shot.

==History==
Alex brought his girlfriend to Gibby's house after she was shot three times in the abdomen during a drive-by. He's in a gang and the bullets were meant for him. Gibby and Pete worked on her. However, when Pete figured out Gibby wouldn't be able to help her there, he called an ambulance, despite Alex pulling a gun on him.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
He has a girlfriend who was shot three times in the abdomen during a drive-by.
